beer.beer_description: Brewed in collaboration with Japan’s Nara Brewing. A velvety foundation yields to bold chocolate and roast notes from coffee beans sourced from Melbourne’s Seven Seeds. Vanilla and lactose are added for a smooth, silky creaminess that balance the beer’s intensity and restrained hop bitterness. Yūgen captures the beauty of the universe that is only partially perceived but fully felt.
